item.description:
These Meet Ups have been successful because NO particular agenda and NO SUCH THING AS BEING LATE.

Get there when ever you can. We all understand there is traffic and lifestyle so people are dropping in (and out) during the event that lasts from 8 pm to 10 pm.

This place roasts their own high-end beans and offers free refills.

Good chance to unwind and enjoy interesting conversation...and drink coffee!
item.name: Holiday Coffee & Talk Event!
